# Ignore everything under reports/ except the archived report bundles that
# back the numbers quoted in README/docs. Keeping the per-panel bundles in
# git lets contributors browse summary.md / results_table.md / judged_samples
# without rerunning the panels. Raw .eval logs stay out of git (too big).
reports/*
!reports/aleval_lcb_min_frontier_models/
!reports/aleval_lcb_min_legacy_models/

